%% Diagram: Location Update Flow
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Driver
    participant WS as WS Gateway
    participant K as Kafka
    participant Loc as Location Svc
    participant R as Redis
    participant H as Cassandra

    loop every 4-5s
        D->>WS: GPS ping
        WS->>K: publish<br/>(partition by H3)
    end
    K->>Loc: consume
    Loc->>Loc: latLngToCell(res 9)
    Loc->>R: ZADD drivers:h3:cell<br/>(TTL 30s)
    Loc->>H: append history
    Note over R: DISCO reads<br/>k-ring → drivers
